                            <comment id="15685562" author="huxi_2b" created="Tue, 22 Nov 2016 03:31:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;During Acceptor initialization, if &quot;Address already in use&quot; error is encountered, the countdown latches for all Processors have no chance to be counted down, hence Kafka server fails to exit, pending when invoking Processor.shutdown&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
